## Giving LLMs Tools
We describe tools to the LLM using a JSON schema, so it knows what it can call and what arguments to provide.

```json
{
  "name": "get_weather",
  "description": "Get current weather",
  "parameters": {
    "type": "object",
    "properties": {
      "location": {"type": "string"}
    }
  }
}
```

